    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Heat</strong> a dry, large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p>\r\n<p><strong>Once</strong> hot, add the pepper and mushroom</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cook</strong> on a high heat for 8-10 min until they've started to char</p>\r\n<p>Tip: This makes them smoky</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
